Question Time host Fiona Bruce will be joined by Conservative MP Mims Davies, Labour MP Jon Ashworth, Liberal Democrats MP Ed Davey, Telegraph journalist Camilla Tominey and entrepreneur Bejay Mulenga. Only minutes into the show, an audience member erupted at the Prime Minister. He said: "Boris Johnson is a proven liar, how can we trust him handling all the problems in the future?" His comment came after the first question of the evening which was "Is it time to move on from 'partygate'?" FOLLOW BELOW FOR LIVE UPDATES...